og.description: A Yardley man walked out of St. Mary Medical Center’s emergency room Saturday and jumped into Lake Luxembourg, leading more than 40 police, firefighters and emergency medical services personnel on an hour-long rescue effort that ended when he was handcuffed to a rescue boat and taken back to the Middletown hospital.
